Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:46.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,还有在镰仓的这间房子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.73,0:00:51.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,本应该是由我和父亲母亲三人一起居住的家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.86,0:00:54.15,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我都知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.37,0:01:02.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,为什么爸爸会放弃作画工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.08,0:01:06.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你是…
