Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.59,0:03:24.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,最近第几代继承名号的歌舞伎演员的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.93,0:03:26.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,什么什么卫门先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.51,0:03:27.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,再努力想想吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.43,0:03:31.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,歌舞伎演员的侧室之子么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.98,0:03:32.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,原来你知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.44,0:03:36.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是呢  毕竟老师个性也挺奇特的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.86,0:03:38.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是稍有差错的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.86,0:03:40.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,说不定老师就变成歌舞伎演员了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.03,0:03:43.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真可笑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.28,0:03:47.83,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,然后  这个是戒澙魁吏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.62,0:03:51.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也就是小姬妈妈的爸爸的画
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.21,0:03:55.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,小姬的外公是个很厉害的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.92,0:03:59.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不忌讳的讲  小姬也是艺术家的血统呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.96,0:04:02.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,歌舞伎演员和日本画的大师啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.47,0:04:08.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老师的婚姻会被反对  比起是因为漫画家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.81,0:04:13.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,更像是被水火不容的艺术家之间的争执所牵连
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.44,0:04:17.15,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也就是说  你的父亲与我的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.52,0:04:19.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是同父异母的兄妹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.86,0:04:22.65,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸有妹妹这件事还是第一次知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.40,0:04:24.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,受打击了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.78,0:04:25.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.07,0:04:26.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不如说…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.03,0:04:31.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,知道我和爸爸是真正的父女  安心了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.33,0:04:34.25,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你还那样想过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.71,0:04:39.29,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\fs80\bord2\c&HF8F6F8&\3c&H6159B9&\pos(904,544)}停
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.00,0:04:40.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,因为爸爸  过于温柔了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.09,0:04:44.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那个事件因为有涉及个人信息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.22,0:04:47.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,请全部通过律师进行确认
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.14,0:04:50.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.52,0:04:54.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:58.44,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我是那一天和后藤先生一起工作的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:04:59.98,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\frx26\fry6\frz331.8\c&H9588C3&\org(918.4,324.8)\pos(705.6,348.8)}周刊文潮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:04:59.98,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\org(859.2,566.4)\frx18\fry6\frz330.9\pos(486.4,540.8)\c&HBA8F80&}记者  千田奈留
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:04:59.98,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\frx18\fry4\frz330.6\pos(296,651.2)\c&H867BBD&\org(670.4,673.6)}有限公司  文潮社
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.98,0:05:02.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是吗  你在调查那次事故啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.69,0:05:06.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,请安心  我不会写成新闻的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.07,0:05:08.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那为什么记者小姐会？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.53,0:05:11.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是我个人感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.20,0:05:12.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,哪怕一点点也好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.29,0:05:15.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是能成为改变现状的契机的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.04,0:05:17.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,虽然公司那边闭口不提
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.42,0:05:20.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但那并不是后藤先生的失误造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.13,0:05:23.59,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an8}周刊少年Jumpo
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.34,0:05:23.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好壮观…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.17,0:05:25.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这些全部都是Jumpo吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.97,0:05:30.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,虽然都在说出版不景气  但还能卖出这么多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.10,0:05:33.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,赶紧收拾了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.58,0:05:57.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,后藤先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.71,0:05:59.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,喂谁快叫下救护车
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.67,0:06:01.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,后藤先生？ 后藤先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.71,0:06:05.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那个货架会失去平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.55,0:06:07.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是因为有人为了看书而偷偷抽去了几册
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.18,0:06:13.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,想要尽快地泄露在网上逞英雄呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.89,0:06:16.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,虽然公司有严令禁止
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:18.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,当然  不是后藤先生干的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.48,0:06:21.69,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,后藤先生说过自己讨厌漫画的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:23.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.19,0:06:27.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就是这间病房的患者吧  我记得
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.90,0:06:30.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是啊  已经过了一年了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.83,0:06:38.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真是讽刺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.54,0:06:43.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,明明逃离了漫画  结果却被漫画所压倒什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.04,0:06:45.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,交了厄运呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.09,0:06:48.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是不是Jumpo  而是Saturday或者漫画人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:51.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也不会堆高到能砸到人的程度了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.51,0:06:53.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.22,0:06:58.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那个时候  他似乎辗转在不习惯的体力劳动之间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.43,0:07:03.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,生活贫困潦倒  都到了必须得卖掉房子的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.36,0:07:05.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,存款的话应该有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.19,0:07:07.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,基本上都花掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.44,0:07:10.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,为了搜寻妻子的下落
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.78,0:07:16.08,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\fad(1100,0)\c&HFFFFFF&\frz350.4\pos(160,73.6)\3c&H30323F&}8人失踪。持续搜索
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.78,0:07:16.08,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\fad(1100,0)\c&HFFFFFF&\frz351.9\pos(1017.6,224)\3c&H2D303D&}事故现场
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.78,0:07:16.08,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\bord2\fad(1100,0)\c&H0F0E10&\3c&H646464&\frx6\fry354\pos(582.8,876.8)\org(600.4,780.8)\frz255}原因调查
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:15.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在小姬出生后不久发生的海难事故
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.95,0:07:20.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,妻子一直下落不明  即便搜索行动结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.96,0:07:22.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,他也自己雇了专业人员
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:25.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,一直坚信着她还活着  继续搜索下去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.21,0:07:28.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,边画着漫画持续了十年以上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.22,0:07:33.55,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,然后在小姬上初中的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.09,0:07:35.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不知道是从哪儿走漏了风声
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.85,0:07:38.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老师他在盼望妻子回来的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.68,0:07:41.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,被周刊杂志当作是美谈而大肆报道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.43,0:07:41.85,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\fade(1400,0)\c&HFFFFFF&\frx6\fry0\frz285.5\move(1122,444,1204,434,0,5402)}有名的漫画家G氏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.43,0:07:41.85,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fade(1400,0)\bord3\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H403D3E&\frx4\fry358\frz22.59\move(2,274,10,300,0,5402)}时至今日依然在等着妻子回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.43,0:07:41.85,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fade(1400,0)\bord3\c&H615D60&\frz24.82\frx24\fry354\move(584,256,666,258,0,5402)}独占新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.43,0:07:41.85,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fade(1400,0)\bord3\c&H4A4848&\3c&HC7C5C6&\frx8\fry356\frz25.6\move(208,960,286,964,0,5402)}作品的背后被隐藏的真实
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.85,0:07:43.10,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\c&H4B4A4A&\pos(254,730)\frx8\fry356\frz23.69}妻子都死了还在画着鸡〇吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.85,0:07:43.10,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\c&H4B4A4A&\frx10\fry358\frz24.74\pos(414,960)}真的无语了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.10,0:07:44.35,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\c&H4B4A4A&\frz334.4\org(1398,596)\pos(360,550)\frx4\fry0}在这种时候  鸡鸡复鸡鸡（）什么的也太不走心了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.10,0:07:44.35,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fs80\c&H4B4A4A&\frx6\fry4\pos(380,572)\org(1036,604)\frz334}当时不还是黄段子的全盛期么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.10,0:07:44.35,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fs75\c&H4B4A4A&\frx4\fry0\frz331.3\pos(-10,986)\org(1028,1032)}作为一个人来说已经完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.35,0:07:46.86,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an8}这家伙画的漫画已经让人笑不出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.23,0:07:51.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,说是不管画什么都无法使人发笑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.57,0:07:53.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老师他封笔了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.95,0:07:58.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,即便如此  「风之紧身裤」还是好好地完结了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.33,0:08:00.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,最终回还挺不错的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.50,0:08:10.51,kakushigoto in 6 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\c&HEFECEE&\frx358\fry10\move(449.2,603.6,452,-450)}全国高中生美术展
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.04,0:08:04.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,结果虽然失去了收入和工作  非常的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:05.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但还是把小姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.46,0:08:10.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,一路顺利地送入了高中了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.26,0:08:12.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是讽刺的是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.93,0:08:18.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,小姬  似乎是好好继承了外公那边的才能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.89,0:08:20.18,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1500)\frz270\pos(666,300)\c&H5C5A51&}高中三年级  后藤姬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.89,0:08:20.18,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1500)\fs50\c&H304C70&\frz270.6\pos(1248,380)}大臣奖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.72,0:08:22.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在做漫画家的时候也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.68,0:08:23.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,辞职了以后也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.23,0:08:26.69,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸在我的面前一直都是笑着的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.44,0:08:28.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真的太过温柔了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.48,0:08:30.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我妈妈说过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.61,0:08:33.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,他一直都非常关心你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.65,0:08:37.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,难道说  把这儿的钥匙给我的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.66,0:08:38.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是我妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.83,0:08:40.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,把这个交给姬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.25,0:08:44.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,如果我出了什么事  用这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.25,0:08:49.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,把房里的东西都卖了  用来供养那孩子的生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:51.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.01,0:08:54.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:09:00.35,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这么说来好奇怪  屋内并没有变空哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.52,0:09:04.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,虽然本人有点难以启齿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.64,0:09:07.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,应该是我妈妈想让你看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.06,0:09:09.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你爸爸的工作成果
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.73,0:09:11.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.82,0:09:14.57,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an8}隐瞒之事  有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.82,0:09:13.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,作画工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:21.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老师他？！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:26.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那么  我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.33,0:09:30.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,虽然我是怕姐姐会哭才来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.50,0:09:31.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不过似乎没事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.25,0:09:33.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.67,0:09:36.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,小姬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.72,0:09:39.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,一子老师  还有各位？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.55,0:09:42.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在这种地方竟然有帅哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:42.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,小雏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.14,0:09:45.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,小姬  你爸爸恢复意识了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.19,0:09:47.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真的假的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.44,0:09:49.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这是好消息吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:52.44,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那  坏消息是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:53.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸他…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.92,0:10:14.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.13,0:10:17.51,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.72,0:10:21.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你是…谁啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.89,0:10:29.44,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,太俗套了吧  记忆丧失啥的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.48,0:10:31.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,即便是漫画这样的分镜草稿也过不了的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.06,0:10:34.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,十丸院先生  这儿是病房
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.36,0:10:36.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老师他才复活呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:37.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,又没去世好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.61,0:10:43.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老师  您忘记小姬了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.95,0:10:46.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我怎么可能会忘记姬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:51.25,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬还只有十岁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.04,0:10:55.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,大概是记忆停留在女儿十岁的时候了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.46,0:10:59.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,最近七年间的记忆似乎不翼而飞了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.55,0:11:02.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,为什么  会是七年前？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.76,0:11:03.76,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.47,0:11:07.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,比如说有什么印象很深的事情之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:10.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,记忆障碍里挺常有的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.69,0:11:14.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,七年前吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.23,0:11:17.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,小姬十岁的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.73,0:11:20.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,有什么那么印象深刻的事情么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.41,0:11:24.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,难道不是最开心的时期吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.16,0:11:26.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,工作也好  私人生活也好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.91,0:11:29.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.62,0:11:32.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,毕竟是我担任责编的时期呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:33.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.63,0:11:35.88,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\c&H6E4A3B&\pos(577.6,633.6)}后藤可久士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.75,0:11:35.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.17,0:11:36.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,快放手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.25,0:11:38.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不好好进行康复训练恢复肌肉的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.67,0:11:39.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是不行的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.13,0:11:40.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.17,0:11:42.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,发生什么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.51,0:11:43.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,他试图逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.18,0:11:46.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我很担心姬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.51,0:11:47.76,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,让我见见姬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.85,0:11:50.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}请稍微冷静一点后藤先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.14,0:11:54.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老师  我能够理解你想见姬的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.31,0:11:57.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但姬见到你现在的这个样子她会担心你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:11:59.44,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.98,0:12:02.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,绝对不能让她看到我这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.16,0:12:05.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,对的  对的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.53,0:12:08.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你先等到康复训练完后也不迟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.37,0:12:12.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,现在您也只有手指能够随意动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.62,0:12:15.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,手指
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.17,0:12:18.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.63,0:12:22.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,至少为了读者  我也得继续画紧身裤的后续了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.22,0:12:26.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那个连载啊  早在…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.01,0:12:28.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,为了圆满完结是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.22,0:12:31.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,他好像以为漫画还在连载
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.14,0:12:33.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,该把真相讲出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.27,0:12:36.44,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这会让他很受打击的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.94,0:12:37.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.56,0:12:39.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这该怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.28,0:12:49.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,为什么会成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.70,0:12:53.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,像这样我们这几个人聚在一起干活不知道是多久以前的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.04,0:12:57.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,没想到我又再次拿起了笔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.71,0:13:03.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这就是爸爸的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.22,0:13:05.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那个  你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.72,0:13:06.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.55,0:13:08.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你是新来的助手吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.97,0:13:11.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.10,0:13:13.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我现在走不开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.06,0:13:16.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真是不好意思啊  我能拜托你一件事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.06,0:13:18.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是什么事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.48,0:13:20.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我很担心我的女儿姬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.98,0:13:23.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,直到帮忙做家务的纳德拉小姐来之前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.82,0:13:25.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我很担心她独自在家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.78,0:13:27.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,所以你能帮我照看一下她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.07,0:13:30.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,之前我也拜托过十丸院
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.03,0:13:32.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,一点用都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.91,0:13:33.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真是过分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.08,0:13:37.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,能够拜托你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.46,0:13:38.83,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.50,0:13:40.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.75,0:13:42.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,离姬回家前还有些时间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.55,0:13:45.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这之前你慢慢来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.97,0:13:46.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.80,0:13:47.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.93,0:13:55.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这之前还有我能够帮忙做的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.23,0:13:57.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.65,0:14:06.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,小姬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.82,0:14:09.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我们来帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.33,0:14:17.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,能问你件事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.41,0:14:22.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,小姬你真的没有注意到你爸爸的隐瞒之事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.80,0:14:26.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我真的不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.59,0:14:31.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就这么一无所知  沉浸在父亲的溺爱之中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.68,0:14:34.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是  我觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.68,0:14:37.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,父亲他一定很喜欢画漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.19,0:14:41.98,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我第一次看到父亲他工作的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.11,0:14:47.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,十分的认真  看上去特别的开心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.78,0:14:52.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,与其重新回想起来再次让父亲失去漫画的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:55.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不如就这样更好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.66,0:14:56.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.45,0:14:59.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你爸爸就会一直把你给忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.83,0:15:04.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,小姬  你觉得这样就好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.63,0:15:06.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.63,0:15:10.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,如果小姬你觉得这样就好的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.93,0:15:11.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.14,0:15:15.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是  你爸爸情况变好了可要给我说哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.22,0:15:19.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,目黑川侦探事务所随时接收委托
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.39,0:15:23.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我也是  要是能够有我帮忙的事情我都会帮的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.19,0:15:26.69,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,毕竟小姬你是我的救世主
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.57,0:15:28.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.41,0:15:35.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.62,0:15:39.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,让你独自一人  真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.04,0:15:48.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,给  十丸院  这周的连载
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.59,0:15:49.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您还在继续画着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.42,0:15:51.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.26,0:15:55.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,居然还真是7年前的后续啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.39,0:15:59.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这一话上的内容基本上和以前画的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.56,0:16:02.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,照这个样子  每周完成原稿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:04.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,七年过后说不定就想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.10,0:16:07.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真的不能够说出真相吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.86,0:16:09.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,都说了会适得其反
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.73,0:16:11.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,得让他自己回想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.53,0:16:15.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我们没事的  为了老师我们会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.53,0:16:18.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,至少你们放过小罗砂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.91,0:16:20.87,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\pos(568,196.8)\frz20.13}周刊少年漫画人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.91,0:16:20.87,kakushigoto in 7 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\c&HC56B63&\3c&H5A556F&\frz298.4\pos(1188.8,366)}涂黑女仆的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.91,0:16:20.87,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\fs40\frz313.9\c&H1C00BE&\b1\pos(793.6,617.6)}大人气感谢！\N\h\h\h{\fs55\c&HE9E9E9&\3c&H2708B0&\b1}刊头彩页
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:20.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,现在她可是我们的招牌作家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:23.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你暂且先帮我把下回给停载了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.92,0:16:27.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,果然老师他很喜欢漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.46,0:16:30.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,画漫画的时候看上去最为开心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.51,0:16:34.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,很久没有看到过那样的老师了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.22,0:16:37.35,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,对于老师而言
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.76,0:16:40.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,让他画漫画就是对他最好的康复训练
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.77,0:16:46.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,各位  听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.36,0:16:48.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:49.98,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.48,0:16:52.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,关于下回故事情节的讨论
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.99,0:16:55.15,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不带上我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.41,0:16:59.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.66,0:17:03.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,大家都挺为老师您着想的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.33,0:17:04.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,都是很好的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.12,0:17:07.83,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.54,0:17:13.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老师您画漫画的时候  看上去特别幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.30,0:17:15.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.18,0:17:20.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您一直以来都隐瞒着自己最爱的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.14,0:17:22.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,到最后不得不放手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.18,0:17:24.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那一定很痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.31,0:17:27.65,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我却没能够注意到这些  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.11,0:17:33.15,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,哪怕一直这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.74,0:17:36.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,只要能够继续画漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.90,0:17:41.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,对于老师您来说  这就是最大的幸福吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.49,0:17:43.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.00,0:17:46.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我最大的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.58,0:17:50.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,和最令我高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.75,0:17:56.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是希望姬能够健康长大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.61,0:18:20.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.45,0:18:21.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.95,0:18:23.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我有事想拜托你们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.45,0:18:24.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,帮帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.83,0:18:28.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我有件东西无论如何也想让我爸爸看到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.33,0:18:31.83,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.63,0:18:34.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.34,0:18:38.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我  果然是个任性得无可救药的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.22,0:18:42.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我果然还是觉得  和爸爸你在一起最好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.40,0:18:55.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,抱歉  突然把你们叫上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.23,0:18:57.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真是见外
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.24,0:19:01.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,目黑川侦探事务所  接下了时隔许久的委托
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.41,0:19:03.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,大家要鼓足干劲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.16,0:19:05.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.25,0:19:15.25,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\frx14\fry26\c&HC8B8A1&\1a&H20&\pos(910.4,56)\org(419.2,-91.2)\frz307.5}江之岛电铁线
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.25,0:19:15.25,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\bord3\frx14\fry26\c&HE8E1E9&\1a&H20&\frz310.9\3c&HA3C45A&\pos(840,393.6)\org(396.8,302.4)}七里之滨站
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.14,0:19:25.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.02,0:19:39.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那么老师  我们差不多该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.07,0:19:41.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,明天我们再来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.90,0:19:42.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.20,0:19:49.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.54,0:19:50.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.54,0:19:51.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.00,0:19:53.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这些箱子是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.92,0:19:54.88,kakushigoto in 2,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\frz326.7\frx22\fry20\pos(1352,424)\org(1665.6,401.6)\b1}风之紧身裤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.38,0:19:56.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是镰仓家里的原稿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.17,0:20:00.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,请看一下这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.10,0:20:06.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.43,0:20:09.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我不记得我有画过这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.14,0:20:11.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,还有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.41,0:20:26.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,终于赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.37,0:20:31.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不枉我们奋战到了最后  这回的故事真有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.66,0:20:33.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那老师  我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.00,0:20:35.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好的  确实收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.04,0:20:40.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,顺带一提  上周的调查问卷也挺普通的不错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.34,0:20:43.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老师  对不起  我擦得太用力了给原稿弄坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.26,0:20:48.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来  今天工作辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.64,0:20:52.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老师  感觉这回的故事的收尾有些差强人意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.02,0:20:55.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这个段子上次好像用过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.35,0:20:57.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我想到了个超级有趣的段子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.15,0:21:00.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,高尔夫俱乐部其实就是蘑菇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.36,0:21:02.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,今天的老师认真得犹如鬼神附体一般
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.07,0:21:04.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,简直就是漫画之鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.74,0:21:06.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.45,0:21:08.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,邪灵退散
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.66,0:21:09.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}你们单纯就是想让我扮鬼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.79,0:21:13.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸来扮鬼  你可以扔在爸爸身上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.29,0:21:17.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,扔在爸爸身上  我做不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.29,0:21:20.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,快看镜头  笑一个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.42,0:21:22.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好难为情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.46,0:21:25.55,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你说些什么啊  这可是一生一次的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.84,0:21:29.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我成为中学生了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.72,0:21:32.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,从今天起  这里就是我们俩的家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.10,0:21:34.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就是稍微有些破旧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.98,0:21:35.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我不介意的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.98,0:21:38.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,只要和爸爸在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.73,0:21:39.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不管是哪里都很好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.90,0:21:41.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.27,0:21:42.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.32,0:21:47.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,今后也请你多多关照  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.24,0:21:52.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.99,0:21:56.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我十八岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.08,0:21:58.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.33,0:22:00.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬
