Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.38,0:22:07.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不要看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.26,0:22:08.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老师他
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.18,0:22:08.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.09,0:22:09.76,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.97,0:22:10.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.93,0:22:11.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,虽然很老套
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.14,0:22:14.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,一点都不好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.77,0:22:17.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸的隐瞒之事就是作画工作
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.56,0:22:21.65,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,最后  我也有隐瞒之事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.48,0:22:21.86,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\frx358\fry348\c&H523F4B&\pos(1294.4,342.4)\org(1428.8,172.8)\frz358.2}美术室
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.82,0:22:26.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬  我说啊  这种东西你在家里画啊
Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.03,0:22:29.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不行不行  你说些什么胡话啊
Dialogue: 1,0:22:29.66,0:22:31.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是让我爸发现了可怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.91,0:22:35.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,暂且先瞒着父亲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.95,0:22:38.25,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,当然  画的不是黄段子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.92,0:22:40.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,说起父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.63,0:22:43.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎么样  这个新企划
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.92,0:22:44.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我要一夜暴富
Dialogue: 1,0:22:45.09,0:22:48.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,把这一年的治疗费用甩在那老头的脸上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.47,0:22:52.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,至今为止都是戒澙魁吏老师援助的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.93,0:22:54.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,人挺好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.31,0:22:56.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎么又是黄段子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.85,0:22:59.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这让小姬知道了  能行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.44,0:23:01.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,毕竟  姬也长大了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.27,0:23:03.15,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,应该不会在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.81,0:23:06.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,干脆画个关于漫画家故事的怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.44,0:23:09.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,黄段子漫画家对女儿隐瞒自己的工作的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.95,0:23:11.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,谁会读这种故事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.16,0:23:13.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我感觉挺有趣的
Dialogue: 1,0:23:13.99,0:23:15.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,还能够以老师您自己为原型
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.04,0:23:17.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,挺能干的嘛  十丸院先生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.83,0:23:20.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这里可是我的工作室诶
Dialogue: 1,0:23:25.88,0:23:28.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你的隐瞒之事是什么呢
